OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy and windy with rain over
OL,6,Fthe Western Isles for much of the day,
OL,7,Fdrier spells developing later.
OL,8,FElsewhere will be dry with light
OL,9,Fwinds, mostly cloudy but with bright
OL,10,Fand sunny spells.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy over the Western Isles
OL,13,Fwith rain, which may be heavy at times
OL,14,Fovernight. Elsewhere will be dry and
OL,15,Fmostly cloudy but some clear spells.
OL,16,FStrong winds easing in west.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,19,Facross all parts. The most persistent
OL,20,Frain however will be in the west with
OL,21,Flonger dry spells further east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
